WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes窶ｦ

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 36]

02:50.220 --> 02:52.000
I want you to tell the Divine Region

02:52.660 --> 02:54.980
that Supreme Deity Xing Yue will marry into the Demon Race.

02:55.010 --> 02:55.920
Ten days later,

02:56.470 --> 02:57.870
she will marry me.

02:59.680 --> 03:00.520
What did you say?

03:02.880 --> 03:03.710
Your memories...

03:03.710 --> 03:04.960
Killing you, hurting you,

03:05.260 --> 03:06.840
or being killed by you

03:06.960 --> 03:08.310
are all such boring options.

03:08.490 --> 03:11.420
You're the high and mighty Supreme Deity Xing Yue who looks down on the world.

03:12.090 --> 03:13.980
If you married me,

03:14.220 --> 03:16.870
it'd be the greatest humiliation for you, no?

03:19.690 --> 03:20.600
Of course,

03:21.579 --> 03:23.190
you can also refuse.

03:24.210 --> 03:25.690
But ten days later,

03:25.970 --> 03:27.930
the wedding will be replaced by Chang Qing's death.

03:27.950 --> 03:29.760
No matter which ceremony it is,

03:30.020 --> 03:31.760
I'm willing to witness it.

03:33.370 --> 03:34.750
A life,

03:35.000 --> 03:36.590
or a wedding.

03:36.760 --> 03:38.440
Make your choice.

03:42.420 --> 03:44.160
After my wedding,

03:44.540 --> 03:45.540
ten days later,

03:46.400 --> 03:48.350
would you break your promise?

03:49.120 --> 03:51.260
Are you really willing to marry me?

03:53.210 --> 03:54.050
Yes.

03:54.300 --> 03:55.410
Aren't you Supreme Deity Xing Yue,

03:55.440 --> 03:57.670
who treats all beings as ants?

03:57.690 --> 03:59.620
Does his life deserve you making such a mockery of yourself?

04:01.760 --> 04:03.710
Chang Qing fell to the Demon Race

04:03.730 --> 04:06.370
due to the karma I planted three years ago.

04:07.020 --> 04:08.740
The peace in the Divine Region is precious.

04:08.770 --> 04:10.450
But the lives of all beings in the world

04:10.480 --> 04:11.640
are also precious.

04:11.660 --> 04:14.130
Since you're still bothered by what happened back then,

04:14.160 --> 04:16.680
I'll give you what you want.

04:19.360 --> 04:21.399
It's just a wedding.

04:24.140 --> 04:27.340
The lives of all beings are also precious, you said.

04:27.370 --> 04:31.290
What a benevolent and loving goddess you are.

04:37.210 --> 04:38.330
Ten days later,

04:38.360 --> 04:40.010
our wedding will commence.

04:40.030 --> 04:41.620
The Divine Region must celebrate with us.

04:44.990 --> 04:47.180
Even if you have only hatred left for me,

04:47.330 --> 04:49.210
I'll be able to stay

04:49.230 --> 04:51.500
by your side like this before I disappear.

04:52.070 --> 04:53.870
Even if it's only for ten days,

04:53.890 --> 04:54.890
it's fine.

05:05.360 --> 05:06.920
I didn't expect you to sleep so well

05:06.920 --> 05:08.310
in the Demon Race's territory.

05:14.140 --> 05:16.230
I've been waiting here for a long time.

05:19.830 --> 05:22.630
[Invitation]

05:20.050 --> 05:22.490
These are all the wedding invitation samples prepared by the Elder.

05:24.280 --> 05:25.450
Since you are awake,

05:25.470 --> 05:27.180
you can choose for yourself.

05:40.610 --> 05:42.670
[Invitation]

05:56.580 --> 05:58.040
The demonic realm is cold.

05:58.480 --> 06:00.170
You should take care of your health.

06:00.200 --> 06:02.520
I don't want to marry a sick bride

06:02.540 --> 06:04.390
at the wedding ten days later.

06:09.210 --> 06:10.760
Why do you look so pale?

06:10.980 --> 06:12.470
Are you really sick?

06:14.330 --> 06:15.770
You don't have to worry about me.

06:16.380 --> 06:18.710
I've never stayed outside.

06:19.360 --> 06:20.950
I'm just not used to it.

06:23.790 --> 06:24.610
Is that so?

06:25.080 --> 06:26.350
If that's the case,

06:26.640 --> 06:28.670
you'll get used to it after a few more days.

06:30.310 --> 06:32.080
Since you don't like others to worry about you,

06:32.850 --> 06:34.280
you can choose on your own.

06:41.110 --> 06:42.320
Jing Yuan.

06:42.570 --> 06:44.330
If we can be together,

06:44.420 --> 06:46.350
if we can share the same future,

06:46.380 --> 06:47.740
I think

06:47.760 --> 06:50.120
I would be very happy.

06:52.630 --> 06:55.620
[Invitation]

07:04.340 --> 07:05.580
Hidden Lord, since you're here,

07:06.330 --> 07:07.600
why don't you show yourself?

07:08.670 --> 07:10.310
It's been a century.

07:10.650 --> 07:12.920
Your senses have become sharper, Demon Lord.

07:12.940 --> 07:14.730
The wedding is in three days.

07:15.020 --> 07:16.500
It's too early for you

07:17.120 --> 07:18.370
to come here now.

07:18.400 --> 07:20.210
Why are you playing dumb?

07:20.550 --> 07:22.340
Back then, we had a deal.

07:22.370 --> 07:23.950
When I fought Xing Yue,

07:23.950 --> 07:25.610
you'd take the chance to destroy the Xing Yue Divine Bow,

07:25.640 --> 07:28.200
and we'd rule over the Divine Region together after that.

07:28.690 --> 07:30.330
But you broke your promise

07:30.620 --> 07:33.510
and wasted my great opportunity.

07:33.540 --> 07:35.210
I did promise to destroy

07:35.230 --> 07:36.790
the Xing Yue Divine Bow with you.

07:37.050 --> 07:38.950
But I also mentioned that

07:39.220 --> 07:40.120
we'd depend on our own abilities

07:40.150 --> 07:41.220
to destroy the bow.

07:41.560 --> 07:43.659
The winner would become the ruler of the Divine Region.

07:44.500 --> 07:45.730
But neither of us succeeded.

07:45.760 --> 07:46.880
Therefore, the deal is off.

07:46.909 --> 07:48.600
Besides, it's been a hundred years.

07:49.370 --> 07:51.320
I'm afraid you didn't come here

07:51.340 --> 07:52.860
for that matter.

07:53.500 --> 07:55.090
I'm here today

07:55.120 --> 07:56.960
to take Xing Yue away.

07:59.010 --> 08:01.340
She's going to be my bride.

08:06.140 --> 08:07.940
Stop lying to yourself.

08:07.970 --> 08:09.410
She won't fall in love with you.

08:09.430 --> 08:10.900
Otherwise, three years ago,

08:10.930 --> 08:12.320
you wouldn't have ended up

08:12.340 --> 08:14.110
in that pitiful state in the Lunar Hidden Sea.

08:15.520 --> 08:16.760
How did you know about that?

08:16.920 --> 08:18.560
I have never ever

08:19.180 --> 08:22.330
let her out of my sight.

08:25.840 --> 08:27.490
Then your eyes

08:28.320 --> 08:29.970
are no longer needed.

08:38.520 --> 08:39.490
Stop.

08:43.260 --> 08:44.890
This is the territory of the Demon Race.

08:44.910 --> 08:46.250
It's not appropriate for you

08:46.610 --> 08:48.000
to start a fight here, Hidden Lord.

08:48.020 --> 08:49.540
Before I came here,

08:49.570 --> 08:51.740
I've rescued Chang Qing back to the Lunar Race.

08:53.630 --> 08:55.210
Come with me.

08:55.680 --> 08:56.320
Really?

08:59.280 --> 09:00.640
I always

09:00.660 --> 09:02.270
have a plan for everything.

09:06.680 --> 09:08.330
Looks like the wedding in three days

09:08.360 --> 09:10.040
should be held in the Lunar Race's territory.

09:10.060 --> 09:11.830
And the person I'll be marrying

09:12.370 --> 09:14.110
won't be you, Demon Lord.

09:15.310 --> 09:22.010
笙ｫIf the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers笙ｫ

09:22.590 --> 09:28.470
笙ｫThe moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place笙ｫ

09:25.750 --> 09:26.860
Three days later,

09:26.880 --> 09:28.520
a wedding will be held at the Lunar Hidden Sea.

09:28.550 --> 09:30.060
Hidden Lord,

09:29.900 --> 09:32.770
笙ｫAs the wind stirs, the clouds gather笙ｫ

09:30.210 --> 09:31.920
would you be my groom?

09:33.840 --> 09:37.190
笙ｫAs the clouds shift, the moon becomes full笙ｫ

09:35.760 --> 09:37.320
I'd love to.

09:37.810 --> 09:43.850
笙ｫLove is the hardest thing to understand笙ｫ

09:38.800 --> 09:39.640
Xing Yue!

09:40.760 --> 09:43.060
Shouldn't you give me an explanation?

09:43.770 --> 09:45.450
Is this your so-called

09:44.520 --> 09:51.360
笙ｫI'm finally back to where it all started笙ｫ

09:45.480 --> 09:46.530
"All beings are equal"?

09:51.620 --> 09:53.280
He is so persistent.

09:52.160 --> 09:58.410
笙ｫAll the answers are already explained笙ｫ

09:53.710 --> 09:55.970
Don窶冲 you want to teach him a lesson?

09:57.800 --> 09:59.260
I always

09:59.290 --> 10:01.340
settle my own business.

09:59.530 --> 10:02.240
笙ｫI'll owe you all of my life笙ｫ

10:03.000 --> 10:06.120
笙ｫBut we're destined to part笙ｫ

10:06.810 --> 10:12.910
笙ｫHow can I downplay this?笙ｫ

10:13.630 --> 10:16.810
笙ｫWhen you engrave your love into my heart笙ｫ

10:17.310 --> 10:20.240
笙ｫWhen my star falls only for you笙ｫ

10:21.520 --> 10:22.700
笙ｫWhen the heavens fall笙ｫ

10:22.650 --> 10:25.600
You forcefully separated the stellar power from the Purple Moon.

10:23.150 --> 10:28.010
笙ｫI can still connect with you through the waning moon笙ｫ

10:25.760 --> 10:27.660
Your primal power is still damaged.

10:27.680 --> 10:29.290
I advise you not to act recklessly.

10:28.840 --> 10:31.360
笙ｫWhen my pain blurs my eyes笙ｫ

10:29.590 --> 10:31.780
I told you three years ago.

10:31.810 --> 10:34.420
Your hundred years of companionship

10:31.950 --> 10:35.920
笙ｫOut of the countless stars, I see only you笙ｫ

10:34.440 --> 10:35.670
was nothing to me.

10:36.570 --> 10:45.430
笙ｫAs you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart笙ｫ

10:37.920 --> 10:40.130
Why do you have to humiliate yourself?

10:45.820 --> 10:47.950
Xing Yue!

11:21.390 --> 11:22.600
Thank you

11:22.600 --> 11:24.580
for solving the problem for me.

11:24.890 --> 11:26.480
I'm really curious.

11:26.510 --> 11:28.550
You were trapped there by him

11:28.570 --> 11:30.620
merely because of Chang Qing?

11:30.650 --> 11:32.010
If I hadn't shown up,

11:32.650 --> 11:34.650
were you really going to marry him?

11:35.220 --> 11:37.380
He broke out of the Demon Race's secret realm.

11:37.410 --> 11:39.530
I had to stay by his side

11:39.550 --> 11:41.830
to find out how powerful he was.

11:42.060 --> 11:43.810
Jing Yuan's feelings for you

11:43.840 --> 11:45.600
are unmatched even by me.

11:45.920 --> 11:48.760
Were you not even a little touched?

11:50.540 --> 11:52.020
Haven't you seen

11:52.440 --> 11:54.390
how I treated him just now?

11:56.150 --> 11:58.920
As expected of the deity with a heart of stone.

11:59.100 --> 12:00.550
In the Divine Region,

12:00.900 --> 12:02.930
only I deserve you.

12:04.410 --> 12:05.650
Only you

12:05.670 --> 12:07.710
deserve to stand by my side too.

12:09.190 --> 12:10.520
Three days later,

12:10.550 --> 12:11.790
the Lunar Hidden Sea

12:11.900 --> 12:13.570
will host our wedding ceremony.

12:33.210 --> 12:33.910
Lunar Lord!

12:35.350 --> 12:36.830
How is Jing Yuan?

12:36.860 --> 12:37.940
Your current vessel

12:37.960 --> 12:39.510
can barely utilize one-tenth

12:39.510 --> 12:40.440
of the Divine Bow's power.

12:40.930 --> 12:42.260
The Demon Lord is fine.

12:42.930 --> 12:44.910
I have sent him into the Demon Race's

12:45.220 --> 12:47.330
secret realm according to your order.

12:47.360 --> 12:49.970
He was just too shocked

12:50.110 --> 12:51.510
to notice it just now.

12:52.240 --> 12:53.360
When he wakes up,

12:53.380 --> 12:55.990
he'll notice that the arrow I shot him with

12:56.150 --> 12:57.890
has little divine power left.

12:58.260 --> 13:00.100
Mo Li has almost mastered his evil techniques.

13:00.130 --> 13:02.430
He won't easily leave the altar of the Hidden Race until then.

13:03.500 --> 13:06.170
Only by letting him see me shoot Jing Yuan

13:06.200 --> 13:07.120
can he believe

13:07.120 --> 13:08.750
that the wedding at the Lunar Hidden Sea is real.

13:08.750 --> 13:10.390
This way, I can use the Lunar Hidden Sea

13:10.390 --> 13:11.400
to trap him

13:11.430 --> 13:12.580
and slay him.

13:13.860 --> 13:14.820
Xiu Yan.

13:15.720 --> 13:16.900
You did a good job.

13:20.520 --> 13:21.430
Lunar Lord,

13:21.450 --> 13:23.070
if you are trapped with the Demon Race

13:23.150 --> 13:25.300
and cannot return to the Xing Yue altar to seal the contemplations,

13:25.330 --> 13:27.260
your power will disappear even faster.

13:27.410 --> 13:28.740
I know.

13:28.820 --> 13:31.550
I can feel the divine power dissipating in my body.

13:31.960 --> 13:33.630
I don't have much time left.

13:33.660 --> 13:34.990
Lunar Lord...

13:35.940 --> 13:36.940
Don't be sad.

13:37.760 --> 13:39.150
Even deities

13:39.440 --> 13:41.160
will perish one day.

13:41.480 --> 13:43.090
But before I perish,

13:43.580 --> 13:45.790
I have one last thing to do.

13:46.710 --> 13:49.540
The Xing Yue Bow has sensed the evil aura.

13:50.210 --> 13:52.540
Before I perish, I must find

13:52.570 --> 13:54.700
the person practicing the evil techniques

13:55.060 --> 13:56.010
and kill him.

13:57.850 --> 13:59.450
I need your help.

13:59.480 --> 14:00.510
Lunar Lord,

14:00.530 --> 14:01.450
your order, please.

14:01.880 --> 14:03.200
In the Divine Region,

14:03.220 --> 14:04.690
apart from me,

14:04.710 --> 14:06.480
only Jing Yuan and Mo Li's divine power

14:06.510 --> 14:08.470
can accommodate the divine souls of the Three Races.

14:08.900 --> 14:11.050
So I must visit the Demon Race.

14:11.950 --> 14:14.320
If Jing Yuan is not the one practicing the evil techniques,

14:14.590 --> 14:16.630
the only one left is Mo Li, the Hidden Lord.

14:17.680 --> 14:19.400
I will try to stay with the Demon Race.

14:19.890 --> 14:20.730
And you

14:21.190 --> 14:23.990
need to let the Hidden Lord know that

14:24.020 --> 14:25.430
I'm staying by Jing Yuan's side.

14:26.150 --> 14:26.830
Yes.

14:29.460 --> 14:30.410
Don't worry.

14:31.470 --> 14:32.560
After three days,

14:33.370 --> 14:34.970
everything will be over.

14:35.140 --> 14:36.010
Lunar Lord...

14:36.240 --> 14:38.050
The Demon Lord will wake up in three days.

14:38.080 --> 14:39.430
He will figure out everything.

14:39.450 --> 14:40.270
But by then, you'd already...

14:40.290 --> 14:40.930
Xiu Yan.

14:43.610 --> 14:44.990
I was born as a god.

14:45.410 --> 14:47.500
I should bear the responsibility of all beings.

14:47.920 --> 14:49.150
But as Xing Yue,

14:50.130 --> 14:51.770
I hope he can live.

15:22.290 --> 15:24.900
I see desire in your eyes.

15:25.110 --> 15:27.290
As long as you work for me,

15:27.310 --> 15:29.680
I can help you manifest a divine body.

15:29.930 --> 15:31.370
Are you willing?

15:34.930 --> 15:36.260
Very well.

15:37.680 --> 15:39.110
From now on,

15:39.170 --> 15:41.850
you are my eyes in Xing Yue Pavilion.

15:42.000 --> 15:45.080
Tell me everything that happens in Xing Yue Pavilion.

15:46.120 --> 15:47.680
One day,

15:48.760 --> 15:50.930
you will get what you want.

15:57.550 --> 15:58.970
Three days later,

15:59.270 --> 16:01.620
I'll make the Hidden Race

16:01.640 --> 16:03.600
the only

16:03.980 --> 16:05.810
immortal race in the Divine Region.

16:23.040 --> 16:23.880
Jing Yuan.

16:32.180 --> 16:33.420
Why are you here?

16:34.540 --> 16:36.370
We're getting married soon.

16:36.400 --> 16:37.730
Where else should I be?

16:41.260 --> 16:43.010
This is the invitation I picked.

16:43.040 --> 16:44.050
Isn't it pretty?

16:45.330 --> 16:47.330
[Invitation]

16:51.970 --> 16:52.890
Yes.

16:54.390 --> 16:56.180
Let's use this pattern

16:56.210 --> 16:57.430
to invite the gods

16:57.450 --> 16:58.780
to our wedding.

17:32.250 --> 17:33.340
What are you looking at?

17:35.300 --> 17:36.690
The Purple Moon.

17:37.880 --> 17:39.730
When we were with the Lunar Race,

17:39.990 --> 17:42.680
you often told me that the Demon Race's Purple Moon

17:42.960 --> 17:44.330
was vast and beautiful.

17:44.730 --> 17:46.860
But I was constantly occupied by other things

17:47.200 --> 17:48.980
and never paid attention.

17:49.380 --> 17:50.580
Looking at it tonight,

17:51.020 --> 17:52.420
it truly is beautiful.

17:52.530 --> 17:53.900
Do you like this place?

17:55.340 --> 17:56.460
Yes.

18:01.790 --> 18:03.340
Let's stay here forever, okay?

18:06.890 --> 18:07.880
If you don't like this place,

18:07.880 --> 18:08.540
we can leave together and...

18:08.560 --> 18:09.320
Okay.

18:12.590 --> 18:14.200
Let's stay here forever.

18:18.290 --> 18:19.290
Xing Yue.

18:19.920 --> 18:21.600
Are we really getting married?

18:24.830 --> 18:26.160
Do you know

18:26.500 --> 18:28.500
when I fell in love with you?

18:29.880 --> 18:31.750
When I sent you the fireflies?

18:34.610 --> 18:36.810
When I sought the divine wine for you?

18:38.770 --> 18:41.180
How about when we went to the Lunar Hidden Sea together?

18:41.440 --> 18:43.420
Remember when I said that

18:43.570 --> 18:45.420
I recognized you the moment

18:45.610 --> 18:46.960
you joined the Lunar Race?

18:48.300 --> 18:50.200
Was it love at first sight?

18:51.330 --> 18:52.550
Not really.

18:53.460 --> 18:55.540
That day, when I saw you,

18:55.560 --> 18:57.190
I thought,

18:57.220 --> 18:59.000
"Why is the Demon Lord

18:59.340 --> 19:01.410
doing such a ridiculous thing?"

19:02.450 --> 19:04.010
To destroy the bow,

19:04.090 --> 19:06.650
you were willing to become a mere attendant.

19:07.070 --> 19:08.790
I became a little interested after that.

19:09.780 --> 19:10.690
I get it now.

19:11.020 --> 19:12.820
Supreme Deity Xing Yue

19:13.250 --> 19:14.730
took one glance at me

19:14.750 --> 19:16.060
and caught feelings for me ever since.

19:26.310 --> 19:27.230
Jing Yuan.

19:28.630 --> 19:30.000
I'm very happy.

19:32.510 --> 19:33.510
What are you happy about?

19:34.530 --> 19:35.330
Everything.

19:38.220 --> 19:40.470
Happy that we met and fell in love,

19:41.090 --> 19:43.120
happy that you prepared the invitation for me,

19:44.270 --> 19:45.870
happy that we're admiring the Purple Moon together

19:46.640 --> 19:48.360
Happy that we're getting married soon.

19:49.790 --> 19:50.590
Happy...

19:51.200 --> 19:56.290
笙ｫThe stars light up your eyes笙ｫ

19:58.520 --> 20:02.250
笙ｫYou are the blueprint of my life笙ｫ

20:02.860 --> 20:07.270
笙ｫThe morning breeze and morning dew笙ｫ

20:07.960 --> 20:12.340
笙ｫLet the tears celebrate笙ｫ

20:10.380 --> 20:11.620
Xing Yue.

20:12.260 --> 20:13.460
If this is a dream,

20:13.890 --> 20:17.270
笙ｫWe embrace each other in the sky笙ｫ

20:16.010 --> 20:18.160
I hope I will never wake up.

20:18.090 --> 20:21.730
笙ｫLet's never let go笙ｫ

20:37.820 --> 20:38.820
Jing Yuan.

20:39.510 --> 20:40.990
I'm sorry.

21:40.570 --> 21:42.800
You woke me up.

21:42.940 --> 21:43.830
Yes.

21:44.520 --> 21:46.040
She made a dream for me

21:46.310 --> 21:48.110
and trapped me inside.

21:48.130 --> 21:50.210
But you forcefully woke me up.

21:50.710 --> 21:51.900
Xiu Yan.

21:52.220 --> 21:54.020
What are you and your Lunar Lord

21:54.050 --> 21:55.530
planning to do?

21:55.550 --> 21:57.220
She isn't planning anything.

21:57.610 --> 21:59.180
Maybe she created the dream

21:59.200 --> 22:01.520
to fulfill her wish.

22:01.550 --> 22:02.720
Her wish?

22:04.710 --> 22:05.850
I think

22:06.320 --> 22:07.730
it's just a trick

22:07.760 --> 22:09.720
to manipulate me.

22:10.020 --> 22:11.070
Do you think I would be

22:11.070 --> 22:13.440
deceived by your words again?

22:14.560 --> 22:15.480
Demon Lord.

22:15.850 --> 22:17.000
Didn't you notice that the Xing Yue Divine Bow

22:17.030 --> 22:18.510
didn't really hurt you?

22:25.990 --> 22:27.480
Her divine power has weakened.

22:28.020 --> 22:28.960
Why?

22:31.360 --> 22:32.630
Because of you.

22:32.810 --> 22:34.040
Because of me?

22:34.230 --> 22:36.020
Because she fell in love with you.

22:46.720 --> 22:47.910
Xiu Yan.

22:48.150 --> 22:50.550
This is the funniest joke

22:50.570 --> 22:52.460
I've heard in my long life.

22:53.470 --> 22:54.990
It's thanks to her that

22:55.350 --> 22:56.830
I'm in this state today.

22:57.430 --> 22:58.580
She betrayed me,

22:59.210 --> 23:00.210
hurt me,

23:00.630 --> 23:01.670
and used me.

23:02.460 --> 23:04.210
If this is love,

23:04.570 --> 23:06.370
I think I'll

23:06.920 --> 23:08.330
have to pass.

23:12.230 --> 23:13.820
She did all this

23:13.840 --> 23:15.470
to save your life.

23:16.120 --> 23:17.050
Tell me.

23:18.750 --> 23:20.870
What do you mean by saving my life?

23:21.480 --> 23:24.460
Do you think the Lunar Lord was born heartless?

23:24.850 --> 23:26.330
That's because she has no choice.

23:26.850 --> 23:29.490
The Bow contains the stellar power of heaven.

23:29.520 --> 23:31.850
Only by giving up all her emotions

23:31.890 --> 23:33.440
can she absorb the stellar power into her body

23:33.440 --> 23:34.680
and use the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

23:35.070 --> 23:36.590
Everyone thinks the Contemplation Stone

23:36.590 --> 23:38.270
is a divine object that seals the Divine Bow.

23:38.770 --> 23:39.560
Actually,

23:40.460 --> 23:42.770
it seals the Lunar Lord's humanity.

23:42.790 --> 23:43.750
But now,

23:44.860 --> 23:47.590
the Contemplation Stone can no longer seal her feelings for you.

23:47.610 --> 23:50.510
The stellar power in her body is disappearing day by day.

23:50.590 --> 23:52.650
In the end, she'll even lose her life.

23:52.950 --> 23:54.370
But even in the face of death,

23:54.750 --> 23:56.600
she didn't give up loving you.

23:56.780 --> 23:58.240
What made her give up

23:58.400 --> 24:01.030
is the laws of the Xing Yue Divine Bow

24:01.220 --> 24:02.480
and your survival.

24:04.830 --> 24:06.710
Lunar Lord asked me to hide it from you.

24:07.120 --> 24:11.250
笙ｫNo matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once笙ｫ

24:07.400 --> 24:08.940
But how can I watch her

24:09.000 --> 24:10.680
bear the misunderstanding

24:11.300 --> 24:13.000
and die in misery?

24:13.470 --> 24:18.750
笙ｫBecause love is thrilling笙ｫ

24:14.040 --> 24:14.950
Die?

24:19.620 --> 24:23.030
笙ｫIf you tear open my heart笙ｫ

24:23.440 --> 24:25.090
This is the Contemplation Stone.

24:23.920 --> 24:26.230
笙ｫI can hold you a little tighter笙ｫ

24:26.580 --> 24:28.730
It can break the seal on you

24:26.780 --> 24:31.100
笙ｫThis pain will gradually fade笙ｫ

24:28.930 --> 24:30.600
and remind you of everything.

24:33.100 --> 24:34.290
Xing Yue.

24:33.840 --> 24:37.450
笙ｫTime withers the moonlight笙ｫ

24:34.490 --> 24:36.490
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

24:36.510 --> 24:38.460
and roam the Divine Region with her.

24:37.910 --> 24:40.490
笙ｫAll that's left is pitch darkness笙ｫ

24:38.850 --> 24:40.180
I'll show her sceneries

24:40.550 --> 24:42.480
outside of the Xing Yue Pavilion.

24:40.790 --> 24:42.550
笙ｫI want to tear apart笙ｫ

24:42.590 --> 24:44.650
I want to be with you forever.

24:43.580 --> 24:46.370
笙ｫThis sky for you笙ｫ

24:45.740 --> 24:47.780
Will you be my partner?

24:47.160 --> 24:50.130
笙ｫA lifetime of guarding everything with you笙ｫ

24:49.120 --> 24:50.280
Why?

24:50.300 --> 24:51.990
Why did you kill him?

24:50.350 --> 24:53.820
笙ｫCrossing the abyss to fulfill our vow笙ｫ

24:52.610 --> 24:53.660
This...

24:53.680 --> 24:55.780
is the Heavenly Path.

24:54.060 --> 24:57.470
笙ｫI'll leap without a thought for tomorrow笙ｫ

24:57.060 --> 24:59.350
I'm created by the power of heaven and earth.

24:57.740 --> 25:00.680
笙ｫThis moment feels like forever笙ｫ

24:59.440 --> 25:00.840
My existence

25:01.010 --> 25:03.760
笙ｫI've missed too much time in my life笙ｫ

25:01.470 --> 25:03.230
is the law of the Divine Region.

25:03.930 --> 25:05.590
The Heavenly Path wants him dead.

25:04.070 --> 25:07.930
笙ｫI'll throw myself into this flame for you笙ｫ

25:05.980 --> 25:07.620
Then, I'll keep him alive.

25:08.170 --> 25:10.110
笙ｫEven if I'll perish笙ｫ

25:10.320 --> 25:12.730
笙ｫAt least I can still kiss your face笙ｫ

25:12.960 --> 25:16.220
笙ｫBurn out my waning moon笙ｫ

25:13.440 --> 25:15.160
Hidden Lord is practicing evil techniques.

25:15.190 --> 25:16.840
Lunar Lord agreed to marry him

25:16.700 --> 25:25.000
笙ｫIn exchange for a lifetime of passion笙ｫ

25:16.860 --> 25:18.680
to trap him with the star chain formation

25:18.710 --> 25:19.840
at the Lunar Hidden Sea

25:19.860 --> 25:21.120
and die with him.

25:21.500 --> 25:23.340
She doesn't have much time.

25:23.370 --> 25:25.540
Maybe only you can save her now.

25:27.710 --> 25:28.780
Xing Yue.

25:47.730 --> 25:48.690
Xing Yue.

25:49.120 --> 25:50.960
When the Heavenly Bell stops toiling,

25:50.990 --> 25:52.730
our divine pact will be made,

25:53.190 --> 25:55.090
and you'll become my wife.

25:56.160 --> 25:57.650
From now on,

25:57.870 --> 26:00.590
I'll take charge of the Divine Region with you.

26:00.610 --> 26:02.070
I won't let you down.

26:23.940 --> 26:25.710
You want to kill me?

26:25.730 --> 26:26.840
Mo Li.

26:26.870 --> 26:29.480
You cultivated evil techniques and killed the Divine Race.

26:29.510 --> 26:30.720
Heaven and earth cannot tolerate you.

26:30.950 --> 26:32.520
Heaven and earth cannot tolerate me?

26:32.540 --> 26:34.100
I'm the heaven and earth.

26:34.130 --> 26:35.890
I'm the ruler of this world.

26:35.910 --> 26:37.910
Who is qualified to sentence me?

26:37.940 --> 26:39.230
The stellar power

26:39.260 --> 26:40.890
and the law of heaven and earth

26:40.910 --> 26:42.580
both uphold peace in the Divine Region.

26:42.610 --> 26:44.290
I, Xing Yue, am qualified.

27:07.550 --> 27:08.700
Your Hidden Power...

27:08.960 --> 27:10.450
As you can see,

27:10.500 --> 27:12.730
I have mastered my techniques.

27:12.960 --> 27:14.490
If you hadn't fallen in love,

27:14.520 --> 27:15.840
you might have been able to kill me.

27:15.860 --> 27:17.270
But you are too weak now.

27:17.290 --> 27:19.970
You can't shoot a full arrow with the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

27:20.000 --> 27:22.110
You are no match for me.

27:23.300 --> 27:24.500
But don't worry.

27:24.530 --> 27:26.130
I won't kill you.

27:26.150 --> 27:27.070
Even if I kill you,

27:27.100 --> 27:29.580
a new Xing Yue will take your place.

27:29.660 --> 27:32.500
The Xing Yue Divine Bow is my only nemesis.

27:32.530 --> 27:34.530
You must be wondering why I entered

27:34.550 --> 27:36.710
the Lunar Hidden Sea despite knowing your plan.

27:37.060 --> 27:39.240
Because once I make the divine pact with you,

27:39.260 --> 27:41.530
I'll be able to control the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

27:41.560 --> 27:43.020
You invited me into your trap,

27:43.180 --> 27:45.630
so I planned around it.

27:46.240 --> 27:47.630
What else did you do?

27:48.470 --> 27:49.660
The Divine Region

27:49.690 --> 27:51.340
doesn't need any other deities

27:51.360 --> 27:53.190
other than the Hidden Race.

27:53.800 --> 27:54.740
Today,

27:54.770 --> 27:57.850
I'll become the ruler of the world.

27:57.870 --> 27:59.850
It's such a big day.

28:00.060 --> 28:03.330
We need to spill the blood of the Lunar and Demon Race to celebrate.

28:04.170 --> 28:05.560
Mo Li.

28:05.720 --> 28:07.170
You deserve to die!

28:10.630 --> 28:11.670
Xing Yue.

28:11.700 --> 28:14.160
As long as you make a divine pact with me,

28:14.180 --> 28:15.350
my Hidden power can protect

28:15.350 --> 28:16.870
your divine soul from dispersing.

28:16.890 --> 28:18.630
You can live forever

28:18.660 --> 28:20.980
and take charge of the Divine Region with me.

28:21.000 --> 28:22.360
Isn't that good?

28:22.710 --> 28:23.620
Dream on.

28:26.160 --> 28:27.330
It doesn't matter.

28:27.350 --> 28:28.740
After we make the divine pact,

28:28.760 --> 28:29.880
you'll be able to live for a long time.

28:29.900 --> 28:32.220
One day, you will change your mind.

28:46.290 --> 28:47.970
The mark of the Demon Lord?

28:48.070 --> 28:50.060
When did you make a divine pact with Jing Yuan?

28:50.320 --> 28:51.290
Mo Li.

28:51.310 --> 28:53.230
The divine pact is set.

28:53.250 --> 28:55.760
You can never control the Xing Yue Bow.

28:55.810 --> 28:58.010
Even if you kill everyone in the Divine Region today,

28:58.040 --> 28:59.390
one day,

28:59.410 --> 29:02.500
the new Lunar Lord will be born in the world.

29:02.520 --> 29:03.760
By then,

29:04.050 --> 29:06.070
you will die.

29:06.090 --> 29:08.680
How am I inferior to Jing Yuan?

29:08.940 --> 29:12.180
You chose him and treated me as the inferior one.

29:13.160 --> 29:16.300
You don't deserve to be compared with him.

29:23.990 --> 29:26.430
I respected you and loved you,

29:26.830 --> 29:29.140
So I put up with you and cherished you.

29:29.290 --> 29:32.040
Since you abandoned me and chose someone else,

29:32.610 --> 29:34.550
don't blame me for being ruthless.

30:01.990 --> 30:03.060
Jing Yuan.

30:03.090 --> 30:04.560
No matter what happens today,

30:04.980 --> 30:06.730
don't face it alone anymore.

30:06.920 --> 30:07.570
I'm here for you.

30:09.270 --> 30:10.710
I'm willing to die with you.

30:11.030 --> 30:12.610
But I refuse to survive alone.

30:13.220 --> 30:13.980
Fine.

30:14.570 --> 30:16.680
Since you want to die,

30:16.850 --> 30:19.030
I'll grant your wish.

30:34.080 --> 30:35.760
After today,

30:35.960 --> 30:39.130
the whole world will regard me as the master.

31:22.860 --> 31:23.800
Jing Yuan!

31:38.540 --> 31:39.590
Xing Yue!

31:39.620 --> 31:40.780
Draw the bow!

31:44.540 --> 31:45.410
Jing Yuan!

31:45.440 --> 31:46.680
Do you want to die?

31:46.700 --> 31:47.940
Xing Yue!

31:47.960 --> 31:49.680
You're the Supreme Deity of the Lunar Race.

31:49.980 --> 31:51.220
Draw the bow!

31:58.410 --> 31:59.780
Hurry, Xing Yue!

32:12.150 --> 32:13.340
Draw the bow!

34:03.410 --> 34:06.200
Do you think you can kill me like this?

34:06.970 --> 34:07.780
No!

34:08.800 --> 34:10.610
My Hidden Heart is still there.

34:11.250 --> 34:13.060
I will destroy the Divine Region,

34:13.090 --> 34:14.340
the world,

34:14.370 --> 34:15.870
and everything!

34:16.440 --> 34:18.420
None of you

34:18.989 --> 34:20.909
will get what you want!

34:50.120 --> 34:55.080
笙ｫWhat kind of flower would never bear fruit?笙ｫ

34:54.110 --> 34:55.429
The Divine Region is destroyed

34:55.570 --> 34:57.130
and the deities are falling.

34:57.150 --> 34:58.730
Sealing this Hidden Heart

34:58.240 --> 35:03.870
笙ｫWhat kind of fruit never sees a flower?笙ｫ

34:59.240 --> 35:01.610
is the last thing I can do.

35:04.520 --> 35:05.610
Jing Yuan!

35:06.530 --> 35:13.960
笙ｫWithstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me笙ｫ

35:14.290 --> 35:15.660
Jing Yuan!

35:14.880 --> 35:19.930
笙ｫI am the fruit to your flowers笙ｫ

35:23.360 --> 35:26.220
笙ｫAcross thousands of miles笙ｫ

35:31.010 --> 35:35.670
笙ｫThe pain of parting lingers笙ｫ

35:38.440 --> 35:45.610
笙ｫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days笙ｫ

35:38.810 --> 35:39.810
Lunar Lord.

35:40.820 --> 35:41.830
Lunar Lord!

35:46.740 --> 35:51.510
笙ｫFlowers in the wind, sand in the water笙ｫ

35:48.360 --> 35:49.210
Lunar Lord.

35:57.840 --> 36:00.060
Hidden Lord's Hidden Heart is too strong.

36:00.220 --> 36:01.790
With my current power,

36:02.010 --> 36:04.110
I can't destroy him completely.

36:04.280 --> 36:06.540
I can only rebuild the Stellar Formation

36:06.980 --> 36:08.030
to suppress the Hidden Heart

36:08.440 --> 36:10.420
under the Lunar Hidden Sea.

36:11.030 --> 36:13.460
You've exhausted your power with your last arrow.

36:13.480 --> 36:15.250
To rebuild the Stellar Formation,

36:15.280 --> 36:16.990
you have to sacrifice yourself for the formation.

36:17.490 --> 36:19.500
But if you die too,

36:19.810 --> 36:21.550
the Divine Region will be gone.

36:21.580 --> 36:23.260
the world is still here,

36:23.660 --> 36:24.720
no?

36:24.910 --> 36:26.780
As long as the Hidden Heart remains,

36:27.330 --> 36:29.620
its threat cannot be removed.

36:31.100 --> 36:32.450
My duty

36:32.480 --> 36:34.300
is to suppress the Hidden Heart.

36:35.030 --> 36:36.370
Xiu Yan,

36:36.490 --> 36:38.150
your mission

36:38.610 --> 36:40.360
is to guard the Hidden Heart

36:40.380 --> 36:42.730
until the birth of the new Lunar Lord.

36:42.830 --> 36:43.630
No.

36:43.650 --> 36:44.400
No...

36:44.430 --> 36:45.500
Lunar Lord...

36:47.750 --> 36:48.590
Lunar Lord!

36:48.620 --> 36:49.510
No!

36:49.540 --> 36:50.580
No!

37:02.810 --> 37:06.780
笙ｫThe flowers flew away笙ｫ

37:10.510 --> 37:14.220
笙ｫMy tears are streaming down like rain笙ｫ

37:18.600 --> 37:25.440
笙ｫLight my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world笙ｫ

37:26.260 --> 37:32.120
笙ｫOn the vast sea, you and I笙ｫ

37:44.970 --> 37:45.780
Remember.

37:46.710 --> 37:49.510
Only the full power of the Xing Yue Divine Bow

37:49.540 --> 37:51.690
can completely destroy the Hidden Heart.

37:51.950 --> 37:53.350
Remember.

37:53.370 --> 37:55.220
Bring everything

37:55.250 --> 37:56.890
back on track.

38:01.940 --> 38:04.710
Lunar Lord!

38:03.650 --> 38:05.550
笙ｫMay I ask, what do the gods see in the world?笙ｫ

38:05.850 --> 38:07.850
笙ｫSadness from infatuation, anger, and parting笙ｫ

38:07.910 --> 38:09.700
笙ｫMy love brought tears笙ｫ

38:09.950 --> 38:11.670
笙ｫGreed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness笙ｫ

38:12.090 --> 38:13.650
笙ｫI was never a flower, but I withered on my own笙ｫ

38:14.130 --> 38:15.550
笙ｫI fell between your brows and became a good fruit笙ｫ

38:15.760 --> 38:17.520
笙ｫThe grand dream of life is hard to let go笙ｫ

38:17.750 --> 38:19.490
笙ｫSearching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing笙ｫ

38:19.980 --> 38:21.510
笙ｫWith a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions笙ｫ

38:21.920 --> 38:23.570
笙ｫI cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon笙ｫ

38:23.840 --> 38:25.950
笙ｫThe daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright笙ｫ

38:26.260 --> 38:27.840
笙ｫThrough the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky笙ｫ

38:27.070 --> 38:28.300
Lunar Lord...

38:28.160 --> 38:29.950
笙ｫI am but a mortal, destined to fade笙ｫ

38:29.140 --> 38:32.370
I will guard the Lunar Hidden Sea and the Hidden Heart

38:30.220 --> 38:32.230
笙ｫBut I went through a thousand calamities for a promise笙ｫ

38:32.520 --> 38:34.020
笙ｫI severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me笙ｫ

38:32.900 --> 38:34.730
with my life.

38:34.220 --> 38:36.680
笙ｫTo protect the world for eternity笙ｫ

38:36.780 --> 38:38.750
Till my final moments.

38:49.650 --> 38:52.420
The Hidden Heart would not destroy where it resided.

38:52.770 --> 38:54.200
So the Lunar Hidden Sea

38:54.500 --> 38:57.400
became the only surviving location of the Divine Region.

39:00.940 --> 39:01.750
Bai Shuo,

39:02.460 --> 39:04.270
you're the one I'm waiting for.

39:07.640 --> 39:08.470
No.

39:08.870 --> 39:11.400
Xing Yue, Jing Yuan, and Mo Li.

39:11.520 --> 39:13.300
They were already dead.

39:13.580 --> 39:15.290
Why can they still appear in the world?

39:15.560 --> 39:17.720
The heaven and earth gave birth to the Supreme Deity of Three Races.

39:17.980 --> 39:19.940
The bodies of the Supreme Deities may live and die,

39:20.330 --> 39:22.320
but the Divine Mantles will never disappear.

39:22.560 --> 39:24.030
As long as the Divine Mantles remain,

39:24.300 --> 39:25.820
they will be able to live again.

39:26.660 --> 39:27.920
However, no one knows

39:28.130 --> 39:30.440
how long that will take.

39:30.760 --> 39:33.360
I'm already lucky that it only took

39:33.450 --> 39:35.170
60,000 years for me to meet you.

39:35.330 --> 39:37.360
But I met Jing Yuan ten years ago.

39:37.380 --> 39:38.980
He was still alive back then.

39:39.010 --> 39:41.580
I cannot understand that either.

39:42.270 --> 39:44.420
Maybe only Jing Yuan

39:44.450 --> 39:46.280
knows the reason.

39:46.300 --> 39:47.700
What about Chong Zhao?

39:47.730 --> 39:48.970
You haven't answered me.

39:49.000 --> 39:51.040
Why was the Hidden Lord born an Eternal Race?

39:51.060 --> 39:52.590
Because fate has been disrupted.

39:53.160 --> 39:54.750
The Fate of Heaven

39:54.770 --> 39:56.600
has been in chaos since

39:56.630 --> 39:58.240
the Divine Region was destroyed,

39:58.660 --> 40:01.310
and couldn't control the whereabouts of your Divine Mantles.

40:01.330 --> 40:03.810
That's why Zhen Yu spent 60,000 years looking for

40:03.840 --> 40:06.580
all of you after escaping the Divine Region.

40:06.750 --> 40:07.670
Zhen Yu?

40:07.960 --> 40:09.440
That black snake

40:09.670 --> 40:10.940
was Zhen Yu.

40:11.450 --> 40:13.740
Back then, his spiritual consciousness was not yet established,

40:13.770 --> 40:15.730
so he couldn't remember your faces.

40:15.970 --> 40:17.660
He only remembered

40:17.690 --> 40:19.190
his faith in the Hidden Lord

40:19.220 --> 40:20.620
and his mission to welcome him back.

40:20.640 --> 40:21.910
It's the same with Luan Zhu.

40:22.560 --> 40:24.610
Thanks to the boundless life energy of the Soul Lotus,

40:24.670 --> 40:25.550
she survived

40:26.030 --> 40:27.680
and ended up on the Eastern Continent.

40:28.150 --> 40:30.080
She hated you for killing Jing Yuan.

40:30.300 --> 40:32.110
So she wanted to kill you too.

40:32.840 --> 40:34.110
I once asked

40:34.700 --> 40:36.220
why she didn窶冲 do it herself

40:36.790 --> 40:38.480
and made Chong Zhao do it instead.

40:38.700 --> 40:41.990
Only a Supreme Deity can truly kill a Supreme Deity.

40:42.440 --> 40:43.880
60,000 years ago,

40:43.900 --> 40:46.720
Xing Yue failed to truly kill Mo Li and Jing Yuan

40:46.920 --> 40:49.080
because her power was too weak.

40:49.110 --> 40:51.500
If Chong Zhao really killed you that day,

40:51.750 --> 40:53.580
your Divine Mantle would have been destroyed

40:53.760 --> 40:55.840
and you'd never live again.

40:56.580 --> 40:57.850
I see.

41:01.400 --> 41:02.400
That's not right.

41:02.970 --> 41:04.220
60,000 years ago,

41:04.250 --> 41:05.880
the Contemplation Stone was in your hands.

41:05.900 --> 41:07.710
You're the only deity who survived.

41:07.740 --> 41:09.780
But why did you say you were dead?

41:09.800 --> 41:11.550
Why did the Contemplation Stone end up in Lanling?

41:12.040 --> 41:13.520
Hidden Lord's attack

41:13.550 --> 41:15.680
hurt me badly.

41:15.700 --> 41:17.340
At that time, I knew

41:17.370 --> 41:18.800
I had little time left.

41:18.830 --> 41:21.360
But I still had my promise to my Lunar Lord.

41:21.820 --> 41:24.860
I didn't want the Divine Region to end its inheritance either.

41:25.090 --> 41:26.010
So,

41:26.040 --> 41:28.090
I also went to the Eastern Continent.

41:30.480 --> 41:32.310
I built a cave there

41:32.690 --> 41:34.720
and carved the secret techniques and history

41:34.750 --> 41:35.630
of the

41:35.650 --> 41:36.570
Divine Region's inheritance

41:36.600 --> 41:38.080
on the stone walls.

41:38.980 --> 41:40.400
At that time, I thought that

41:40.420 --> 41:41.900
maybe one day,

41:41.930 --> 41:44.000
a fated one would stumble upon this cave

41:44.420 --> 41:47.180
and witness the history and former glory

41:47.200 --> 41:48.350
of the Divine Region.

41:48.590 --> 41:49.960
In the Divine War,

41:50.130 --> 41:52.140
the Contemplation Stone went completely silent.

41:52.160 --> 41:54.570
And I sensed that the new Lunar Lord

41:54.590 --> 41:56.500
would be born in the Eastern Continent.

41:56.520 --> 41:58.210
So I gave the Contemplation Stone

41:58.240 --> 42:01.110
to the famous Lanling Clan.

42:02.040 --> 42:03.440
I left a divine edict

42:03.850 --> 42:05.890
to let every sect leader of Lanling

42:05.950 --> 42:07.110
wait for and aid the girl

42:07.110 --> 42:09.440
who could activate the Contemplation Stone.

42:10.280 --> 42:11.400
Unfortunately,

42:11.890 --> 42:14.000
when the secret was passed down to the current generation,

42:14.480 --> 42:16.320
it was used by Jin Yao instead.

42:18.780 --> 42:20.110
After doing all that,

42:20.190 --> 42:21.920
I returned to the Lunar Hidden Sea

42:23.100 --> 42:25.180
and guarded the Hidden Heart without rest.

42:25.740 --> 42:26.530
Soon,

42:27.580 --> 42:29.180
I died from my serious injury.

42:30.610 --> 42:31.920
It was the protection power Lunar Lord

42:31.920 --> 42:33.920
left me in this Flaming Moon pendant

42:34.660 --> 42:36.850
that helped me maintain a strand of my divine soul

42:36.880 --> 42:38.080
to this day.

42:38.670 --> 42:41.360
But why are you only telling me all this now?

42:41.900 --> 42:42.850
Why did you pretend

42:42.880 --> 42:44.360
to be my benefactor on purpose?

42:45.050 --> 42:46.030
Because at that time,

42:46.030 --> 42:48.150
you were just a human who had never experienced the world.

42:48.770 --> 42:50.690
You didn't even know what Eternals and demons were,

42:51.150 --> 42:53.500
let alone understand what it means to protect the world.

42:54.340 --> 42:55.820
Becoming an Eternal to return the favor

42:55.850 --> 42:57.330
became your original intention,

42:57.350 --> 42:59.310
helping you overcome all obstacles along the way.

42:59.820 --> 43:00.740
Now,

43:01.060 --> 43:03.170
you've experienced a lot of life and death

43:03.330 --> 43:04.530
and developed your mind.

43:04.980 --> 43:06.880
You also possess the divine power

43:07.050 --> 43:08.680
to take on the responsibility now.

43:08.750 --> 43:10.360
If I were really a deity,

43:10.450 --> 43:12.220
why couldn't I revive the dead

43:12.250 --> 43:13.520
and save Fan Yue?

43:13.540 --> 43:14.790
I also didn't expect that

43:15.510 --> 43:18.170
Fan Yue would find the cave.

43:18.290 --> 43:19.860
The curse of the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal

43:19.890 --> 43:21.330
wasn窶冲 part of my plan,

43:21.550 --> 43:22.910
and certainly not what I wanted.

43:23.580 --> 43:24.780
Now I can only help you

43:24.800 --> 43:26.630
protect his body.

43:26.670 --> 43:28.020
As for the rest,

43:28.220 --> 43:30.310
I can do nothing.

43:33.640 --> 43:35.000
But, Bai Shuo,

43:35.240 --> 43:36.990
this is not the time to be sad.

43:37.610 --> 43:39.450
I'm telling you everything today

43:39.670 --> 43:42.820
because the Lunar Hidden Sea can no longer suppress the Hidden Heart.

43:42.850 --> 43:44.180
Why?

43:44.200 --> 43:45.510
After 60,000 years,

43:46.020 --> 43:48.450
even the strongest divine power will disappear.

43:49.230 --> 43:52.000
Without Xing Yue and Jing Yuan's powers suppressing it,

43:52.530 --> 43:54.030
the Hidden Heart will escape,

43:54.320 --> 43:56.610
and the Lunar Hidden Sea will no longer exist.

43:56.630 --> 43:59.270
I can only use the Contemplation Stone in your body

43:59.300 --> 44:01.010
to keep the Hidden Heart for now.

44:01.450 --> 44:03.600
But this is not a long-term solution.

44:04.250 --> 44:05.170
Bai Shuo,

44:05.580 --> 44:07.750
you have to find the Xing Yue Divine Bow

44:07.970 --> 44:10.000
and completely destroy Hidden Heart

44:10.170 --> 44:12.510
to avoid the world-destroying catastrophe.
